author: BIGRED1959
title: Veldeer Honeymoon is over
text: Quote: Originally Posted by Cbus cardsfan Veldheer is playing at a pretty high level. Last year, he played at an elite level. He's still good but needs to pick it up because he's shown more in the past. Having a new LG next to him is likely causing some problems as they need time to mesh. LT that play at elite levels should be able to do that from year to year... Many many do... His penalties are troublesome and seriously he should be able to handle the old man in Pittsburgh with relative ease... His performance this year can't simply be because he has a different LG next to him especially considering who that LG is...
